query.sfwSql: SELECT * FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN WHERE ORG_ID=@ORG_ID AND ORG_PLAN_ID <> @ORGPLANID

SELECT ORG.ORG_NAME AS ProviderOrgName,OPP.STATUS_ID,OPP.STATUS_VALUE,OPP.ORG_PLAN_PROVIDER_ID,OPP.ORG_PLAN_ID,OPP.PROVIDER_ORG_ID FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN_PROVIDER OPP LEFT JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ORG.ORG_ID = OPP.PROVIDER_ORG_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_ORG_PLAN OP ON OP.ORG_PLAN_ID=OPP.ORG_PLAN_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_PLAN SP ON SP.PLAN_ID=OP.PLAN_ID WHERE OPP.ORG_PLAN_ID=@ORG_PLAN_ID
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN WHERE ORG_ID=@ORG_ID AND PLAN_ID=12

query.ID: CHECK ATLEAST ONE RETR WHILE RESTRICT
query.sfwSql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN OP INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN SP ON SP.PLAN_ID=OP.PLAN_ID WHERE OP.ORG_ID=@ORG_ID AND SP.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE='RETR'

query.ID: CHECK IF GIVEN PLAN IS OPTIONAL
query.sfwSql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_PLAN_EMP_CATEGORY_CROSSREF PC INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ORG.EMP_CATEGORY_VALUE=PC.EMP_CATEGORY_VALUE AND ORG.ORG_ID=@ORG_ID WHERE PC.PLAN_ID=@PLAN_ID AND PC.REQUIRED_FLAG_OPTION_VALUE='OPTN'
SELECT * FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN OP INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ORG.ORG_ID=OP.ORG_ID AND ORG.ORG_TYPE_VALUE='PRVD' AND ORG.STATUS_VALUE='ACTV' WHERE OP.PLAN_ID=@PLAN_ID
SELECT * FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN OP INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ORG.ORG_ID=OP.ORG_ID AND ORG.ORG_TYPE_VALUE='EMPL' AND ORG.STATUS_VALUE='ACTV' WHERE OP.PLAN_ID=@PLAN_ID
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_PLAN WHERE PLAN_ID=@PLANID AND RETIREMENT_TYPE_VALUE ='DB'

query.ID: IF EMPL ADD DC BEFORE MAIN OR LE
query.sfwSql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN WHERE ORG_ID=@ORG_ID AND PARTICIPATION_END_DATE IS NULL AND ((PLAN_ID=1) OR (PLAN_ID=27) OR (PLAN_ID=2) OR (PLAN_ID=20))

query.ID: CHECK IF GIVEN PLAN IS RESTRICTED
query.sfwSql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_PLAN_EMP_CATEGORY_CROSSREF PC INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ORG.EMP_CATEGORY_VALUE=PC.EMP_CATEGORY_VALUE AND ORG.ORG_ID=@ORG_ID WHERE PC.PLAN_ID=@PLAN_ID AND PC.REQUIRED_FLAG_OPTION_VALUE='REST'

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_PLAN_EMP_CATEGORY_CROSSREF PC INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ORG.EMP_CATEGORY_VALUE=PC.EMP_CATEGORY_VALUE AND ORG_ID=@ORG_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_ORG_PLAN OP ON OP.PLAN_ID=PC.PLAN_ID AND ORG.ORG_ID=OP.ORG_ID AND OP.PARTICIPATION_END_DATE IS NULL WHERE PC.REQUIRED_FLAG_OPTION_VALUE='MAND' AND OP.ORG_PLAN_ID IS NULL
SELECT DISTINCT b.* FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN a INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN b ON a.ORG_ID = @orgId AND a.PLAN_ID = b.PLAN_ID

Select top 1 Org_plan_id,effective_date from sgt_org_plan_dental_rate where org_plan_id in (select Org_plan_id from sgt_org_plan where Org_id=@Org_id and plan_id=@plan_id) and effective_date <= getdate() order by effective_date desc

select top 1 * from sgt_plan_retirement_rate where effective_date in (select max(effective_date) from sgt_plan_retirement_rate where plan_id=@plan_id and member_type_value=@member_type_value and effective_date<=getdate() ) and member_type_value=@member_type_value
Select * from sgt_Org_plan_provider where org_plan_id=@Org_plan_id and status_value='ACTV'
Select * from sgt_org_plan_dental_rate where org_plan_id=@org_plan_id and effective_date=@effective_date

Select top 1 Org_plan_id,effective_date from sgt_Org_Plan_eap_rate where org_plan_id in (select Org_plan_id from sgt_org_plan where Org_id=@Org_id and plan_id=@plan_id) and effective_date <= getdate() order by effective_date desc
Select * from sgt_Org_Plan_eap_rate where org_plan_id=@org_plan_id and effective_date=@effective_date

Select top 1 Org_plan_id,effective_date from SGT_ORG_PLAN_LTC_RATE where org_plan_id in (select Org_plan_id from sgt_org_plan where Org_id=@Org_id and plan_id=@plan_id) and effective_date <= getdate() order by effective_date desc
Select * from SGT_ORG_PLAN_LTC_RATE where org_plan_id=@org_plan_id and effective_date=@effective_date

Select top 1 Org_plan_id,effective_date from SGT_ORG_PLAN_VISION_RATE where org_plan_id in (select Org_plan_id from sgt_org_plan where Org_id=@Org_id and plan_id=@plan_id) and effective_date <= getdate() order by effective_date desc
Select * from SGT_ORG_PLAN_VISION_RATE where org_plan_id=@org_plan_id and effective_date=@effective_date

Select top 1 Org_plan_id,effective_date from SGT_ORG_PLAN_HMO_RATE where org_plan_id in (select Org_plan_id from sgt_org_plan where Org_id=@Org_id and plan_id=@plan_id) and effective_date <= getdate() order by effective_date desc
Select * from SGT_ORG_PLAN_HMO_RATE where org_plan_id=@org_plan_id and effective_date=@effective_date and emp_category_value=@emp_category_value

Select top 1 Org_plan_id,effective_date from SGT_ORG_PLAN_LIFE_RATE where org_plan_id in (select Org_plan_id from sgt_org_plan where Org_id=@Org_id and plan_id=@plan_id) and effective_date <= getdate() order by effective_date desc
Select * from SGT_ORG_PLAN_LIFE_RATE where org_plan_id=@org_plan_id and effective_date=@effective_date

SELECT top 1 a.Org_plan_id,a.effective_date FROM DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE A INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF B ON A.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF_ID = B.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF_ID INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF C ON B.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF_ID = C.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF_ID where a.org_plan_id in (select Org_plan_id from sgt_org_plan where Org_id=@orgid and plan_id=@planid) and a.effective_date <= getdate() AND C.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE=@membertypevalue order by a.effective_date desc

SELECT top 1 a.Org_plan_id,a.effective_date FROM DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE A INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF B ON A.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF_ID = B.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF_ID INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF C ON B.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF_ID = C.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF_ID where a.org_plan_id in (select Org_plan_id from sgt_org_plan where Org_id=@orgid and plan_id=@planid) and a.effective_date <= getdate() AND C.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE=@membertypevalue order by a.effective_date desc
Select * from SGT_ORG_PLAN_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE where org_plan_id=@org_plan_id and effective_date=@effective_date

DECLARE @ALTERNATE_STRUCTURE_CODE_VALUE varchar(25); SELECT @ALTERNATE_STRUCTURE_CODE_VALUE=ALTERNATE_STRUCTURE_CODE_VALUE FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN where org_plan_id=@org_plan_id IF(@ALTERNATE_STRUCTURE_CODE_VALUE='NGRF') Begin SELECT A.* FROM DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE A INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF B ON A.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF_ID = B.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF_ID INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF C ON B.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF_ID = C.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF_ID WHERE C.WELLNESS = CASE WHEN @WELLNESS = 'Y' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AND C.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE=@MEMBER_TYPE_VALUE and isnull(plan_option_value,'')=isnull(@plan_option_value,'') and org_plan_id=@provider_org_plan_id and C.rate_structure_value in (SELECT TOP 1 RATE_STRUCTURE_VALUE FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_STRUCTURE_REF WHERE EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effective_date AND @PlanParticipationDate BETWEEN ISNULL(ENROLLMENT_DATE_FROM,CAST(0 AS DATETIME)) AND ISNULL(ENROLLMENT_DATE_TO,CAST('2999-12-31' AS DATETIME)) AND HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE=@MEMBER_TYPE_VALUE ORDER BY EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) and c.ALTERNATE_STRUCTURE_CODE_VALUE in(SELECT TOP 1 ALTERNATE_STRUCTURE_CODE_VALUE FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_STRUCTURE_REF WHERE EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effective_date AND @PlanParticipationDate BETWEEN ISNULL(ENROLLMENT_DATE_FROM,CAST(0 AS DATETIME)) AND ISNULL(ENROLLMENT_DATE_TO,CAST('2999-12-31' AS DATETIME)) AND HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE=@MEMBER_TYPE_VALUE AND ALTERNATE_STRUCTURE_CODE_VALUE='NGRF' ) End Else Begin SELECT A.*,C.ALTERNATE_STRUCTURE_CODE_VALUE FROM DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE A INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF B ON A.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF_ID = B.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF_ID INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF C ON B.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF_ID = C.ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_REF_ID WHERE C.WELLNESS = CASE WHEN @WELLNESS = 'Y' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AND C.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE=@MEMBER_TYPE_VALUE and isnull(plan_option_value,'')=isnull(@plan_option_value,'') and org_plan_id=@provider_org_plan_id and C.rate_structure_value in (SELECT TOP 1 RATE_STRUCTURE_VALUE FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_RATE_STRUCTURE_REF WHERE EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effective_date AND @PlanParticipationDate BETWEEN ISNULL(ENROLLMENT_DATE_FROM,CAST(0 AS DATETIME)) AND ISNULL(ENROLLMENT_DATE_TO,CAST('2999-12-31' AS DATETIME)) AND HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE=@MEMBER_TYPE_VALUE ORDER BY EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) and isnull(C.ALTERNATE_STRUCTURE_CODE_VALUE,'') <>'NGRF' End

If @benifitTypeValue = 'RETR' or @benifitTypeValue = 'INSR' Begin SELECT * FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN A INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN B ON A.PLAN_ID = B.PLAN_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION O ON O.ORG_ID = A.ORG_ID AND O.ORG_TYPE_VALUE = 'EMPL' AND O.STATUS_VALUE = 'ACTV' left outer join ( Select * from sgt_employer_payroll_header EH where Month(@ParamDate) = Month(Payroll_paid_date) and Year(@ParamDate) = year(Payroll_paid_date) and Eh.status_Value <> 'IGNR' and Report_type_value = 'REG' and Eh.header_type_Value = @benifitTypeValue ) EmpH on EMPH.org_id = O.org_id WHERE B.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = @benifitTypeValue and emph.employer_payroll_header_id is null and A.participation_start_date <= @Paramdate End Else Begin SELECT * FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN A INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN B ON A.PLAN_ID = B.PLAN_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION O ON O.ORG_ID = A.ORG_ID AND O.ORG_TYPE_VALUE = 'EMPL' AND O.STATUS_VALUE = 'ACTV' left outer join ( Select * from sgt_employer_payroll_header EH where @ParamDate between pay_period_start_date and Pay_period_end_date and Eh.status_Value <> 'IGNR' and Report_type_value = 'REG' and Eh.header_type_Value = @benifitTypeValue ) EmpH on EMPH.org_id = O.org_id WHERE B.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = @benifitTypeValue and emph.employer_payroll_header_id is null End
select * from sgt_plan_retirement_rate where effective_date<DATEADD(yy, DATEDIFF(yy,0,getdate()), 0) and member_type_value=@member_type_value order by effective_date
